## Step 2: Place the Limit Order

```typescript
// $58,000 trigger price — scaled to 30 decimals
// $58,000 = 58000 * 10^30
const limitPrice = 58_000n * 10n ** 30n;

// $1,000 collateral in USDC — scaled to 6 decimals
const payAmount = 1_000n * 10n ** 6n; // 1,000,000,000n

const tx = await sdk.orders.long({
  marketAddress,
  payTokenAddress: usdcAddress,       // Paying with USDC
  collateralTokenAddress: usdcAddress, // USDC collateral (common for longs too)
  payAmount,                           // 1,000 USDC
  leverage: 10_000n,                   // 1x leverage (no leverage on the $1,000)
  limitPrice,                          // Triggers when BTC <= $58,000
  allowedSlippageBps: 100,             // 1% slippage tolerance
  skipSimulation: true,
});

