---

**What you might be looking for:**

- **Swap SOL on Solana** → Use a Solana-native DEX like [Jupiter](https://jup.ag) or [Raydium](https://raydium.io)
- **Swap ETH or ARB to USDC on Arbitrum** → GMX can do this:

```typescript
const { GmxSdk } = require("@gmx-io/sdk");

const sdk = new GmxSdk({
  chainId: 42161, // Arbitrum
  rpcUrl: "https://arb1.arbitrum.io/rpc",
  oracleUrl: "https://arbitrum-api.gmxinfra.io",
  subsquidUrl: "https://gmx.squids.live/gmx-synthetics-arbitrum:prod/api/graphql",
  account: "0xYourAddress",
  walletClient, // viem WalletClient
});

const { tokensData } = await sdk.markets.getMarketsInfo();

const wethAddress = Object.values(tokensData).find(t => t.symbol === "WETH")?.address;
const usdcAddress = Object.values(tokensData).find(t => t.symbol === "USDC")?.address;

await sdk.orders.swap({
  fromTokenAddress: wethAddress,
  toTokenAddress: usdcAddress,
  fromAmount: 1_000000000000000000n, // 1 ETH (18 decimals)
  allowedSlippageBps: 100, // 1% slippage
});
```

